  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'=
>Asteroids
  are r</span>ocky debris, often rich with metal ores. Larger asteroids can
  conceal extensive networks of tunnels and caves. </p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>They can be found in most star systems, often alone,=
 but sometimes
  as part of large asteroid fields.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Asteroids cannot be colonized.<span lang=3DEN-GB
